CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 10, 1967, pg. 17, reads: "Uganda Table - This table was one of many that was used to represent an African country. A glance can show the group was enjoying themselves."
TitMainTitle: Women and men, including Beatrice Vasser, Ted Vasser, Bob Nicklos, Lee Bertha Nicklos, and Barbara Calloway, in the Flying Carpet for Alpha Kappa Alpha "Ajoyo"
